# Integration with Maven Project

Step 1: Generate Token  
Go to Sonar Dashboard → My Account → Security → Generate Token  

Step 2: Clone Project  
https://github.com/ashokitschool/SB-REST-H2-DB-APP  

Step 3: Update pom.xml  

Add below inside <properties>:

<properties>
  <sonar.host.url>http://<your-ip>:9000/</sonar.host.url>
  <sonar.login><your-token></sonar.login>
</properties>

Step 4: Run Command  

mvn sonar:sonar  

